  <text>
    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">三人目の患者は、</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">いかにもつかれきつた風をして、</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">べろりと舌をたらした、</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">お醫者が小鼻をとんがらして、</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">『氣分はどうです』</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">『よろしい』</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">『食物は』</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">『おいしい』</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">『それから……』</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">『それからすべてよろしい』</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">そして患者は椅子からとびあがつた、</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">みろ、歪んだ脊髓のへんから、</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">ひものやうにぶらさがつた、</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">なめくじの神經だの、くさつた<seg rend="sesame_dot" rendition="em">くらげ</seg>の手くびだの……。</seg>
<seg rend="burasage" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em; text-indent: -1em;">そいつは<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">眞赤</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">まつか</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>の<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">殺人者</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">ひとごろし</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>だ。</seg>
<lb />
<lb />
</seg></p></body>
